data.description: Introducing a stunning property with water view on your backyard. The residence features multiple spacious rooms and bedrooms with tile floor throughout the first floor.  The updated kitchen is equipped with modern appliances perfect for those who love to cook and entertain. It opens up to an expansive living area where you can welcome company or simply unwind after a long day.  Outdoors, immerse in serenity within your private yard adorned with lusciously green landscaping with a great view and just perfect for barbecue parties or an outdoor relaxation hub. Home location is also conveniently close to shopping centers, UCF, Lake Nona Medical City, and main highways allowing easy access to various amenities.
